<p><a name="Published_peer-reviewed_studies" id="Published_peer-reviewed_studies"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Snus&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Published peer-reviewed studies">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Published peer-reviewed studies</span></h2>
<ul>
